00076 // Inserts an element into the map.
00077 
00078 // @returns A pair whose bool component is true if an insertion was
00079 //          made and false if the map already contained an element
00080 //          associated with that key, and whose iterator component coresponds to
00081 //          the address where a new element was inserted or where the element
00082 //          was already located.
00083 std::pair<TreeMap::iterator, bool> TreeMap::insert(const std::pair<Key, Val>& entry)
00084 {
00086    iterator i;
00087    for(i=begin(); i!=end(); ++i)
00088    {
00089       if(i->first==entry.first)
00090         return std::make_pair(i, (bool)false);
00091    }
00092         return std::make_pair(i, (bool)false);
00093 }
